\newlabel{fig:damaged_CPW}{{23}{32}{Example of a damaged CPW after the mounting process. The scratches to the CPW lines are visible, which completely compromised the functionality of the CPW. The damage was done during testing for shorted contacts.\relax }{figure.caption.23}{}}
